headline: TKO Group Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: TKO Group (NYSE:TKO) executives used the company’s fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 earnings call to highlight a year they described as “catalytic,” marked by major U.S. media rights renewals, stronger profitability, and an expanded capital return program.
